libxft: the X Font library
libxft:
libxft: The current version of Xft (2.0) provides a client-side font API
libxft: for X applications. It uses Fontconfig to select fonts and the X
libxft: protocol for rendering them. When available, Xft uses the Render
libxft: extension to accelerate text drawing. When Render is not available,
libxft: Xft uses the core protocol to draw client-side glyphs. This
libxft: provides completely compatible support of client-side fonts for
libxft: all X servers.
